make sure your system is up to date:
sudo pacman -Syu

another prerequisite for the aur:
sudo pacman -S git base-devel

installing git skip if youve already installed git:
sudo pacman -S git

getting files:
git clone https://aur.archlinux.org/yay.git

switching directory:
cd yay

making the package:
makepkg -si

then you can use yay -S to install things

